  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad-\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0db4\u0dd4 \u0d8b\u0db4  \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Former Vice Chairman of Kotikawatta-Mulleria Assembly shot dead",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sumudu Rukshan (40), the former Vice Chairman of Kotikawatta Mulleriya Pradeshiya Sabha, was shot dead today (2) afternoon at Mulleriya Bank junction by two persons who came on a motorcycle, Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Mr. Nihal Talduwa said.",
        "Police also say that Mr. Rukshan, who served as a member of the local council until his death, is a nephew of Karate Dhammika, an underworld leader.",
        "It is said from police sources that information has been revealed to the police regarding an alleged incident where the district head, who is considered to be a follower of the underworld leader Angoda Lokka, has been threatened.",
        "Mulleriya police officers are conducting investigations to arrest the suspects involved in the incident."
      ],
